These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
House: futuristic, wooden
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the wooden house is not to the right of the wooden house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| House   | wooden | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person drinking water##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, february
1. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
3. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Birthday   | november | february |

 #################################

 
